      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sad-04.m4a",
      "text": "でも最近は聞いてくれなくってさー……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But lately she hasn't been listening~…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.8666349409,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-05.m4a",
      "text": "その悩みとは、現在向き合い中なの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm currently working on facing that worry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 246.8182225057,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_01-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "……俺でも話を聞くくらいは出来るから\n悩んでいることがあったら、相談してくれよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I can at least listen to you if you need to talk‚\nSo if you're ever troubled‚ talk to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 252.6666278201,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_surp-04.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、本当？　じゃあ～……はい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ really? Then~… Here goes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 256.2666278201,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_start-03.m4a",
      "text": "大晦日は、番組の最後まで会場にいたいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to stay at the venue until the end of the show on New Year's Eve!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 260.2554080738,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_01-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "ダメだ。翌日の元旦も仕事があるだろ？\n出番が終わったら、帰って次の日に備えないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No way. You have work on New Year's Day‚ too‚ right?\nYou need to go home after your performance and prepare for the next day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 267.5666206995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_surp-06.m4a",
      "text": "え～！　なんでも相談しろって言ったのに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh~! You said I could talk to you about anything!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 271.4999540328,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-07.m4a",
      "text": "頑固！　ケチ！　諦めないからねっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Stubborn! Stingy! I won't give up!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 274.5276163616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_01-koh020.m4a",
      "text": "年に一度のお祭り番組だし、そりゃ最後までいたいよな\nでも、出来るだけ休んでほしいんだ。ごめん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a once-a-year festival program‚ of course you want to stay till the end.\nBut I want you to rest as much as possible. I'm sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 283.1999804814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-06.m4a",
      "text": "そんなの大丈夫なのに～～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's okay!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 286.7666471481,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sad-01.m4a",
      "text": "というか、それだけじゃないんだけどなー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not just that‚ though~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 289.3328146905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_01-koh021.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　他にも理由があるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Is there another reason?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 292.5000048954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "知らないっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't know!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 296.1666715621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-13.m4a",
      "text": "も～！　事務所に戻るのは歌ってからにする！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh~! I'm not going back to the office until I sing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 297.7143339302,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}